+
+**Voice Rule:** Color is never arbitrary. Every color reference anchors the reader in Oz's geography or signals narrative meaning. Use the Oz color-map consistently: green = Emerald City, yellow = Winkie, blue = Munchkin, red = Quadling, purple = Gillikin.
+
+**Frequency:** 1,200+ color references across 211k words. Roughly 6/1k words. Every scene is color-anchored.
