+Find slugs:
+```bash
+php artisan tinker --execute='foreach(["Wizard","Sherlock","Anima"] as $t){ $s=App\Models\Story::where("title","like","%{$t}%")->first(); echo ($s?->slug ?? "NOT FOUND")." — {$t}".PHP_EOL; }'
